<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Valid DHL Packstation</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Orders are filtered that contain a valid DHL Packstation as the delivery address.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Faulty DHL Packstation</strong></p></td>
