</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Shipping costs (gross)</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Orders are filtered according to the gross shipping costs. You can enter a value and assign an operator to it.<br>
For further information, refer to the <a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures#configuration">example configuration</a> in section 1.3.3.</p></td>
