<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Split into orders by item availability</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Same as the procedure above. Orders are split into orders by item availability.</p></td>
