<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Orders are automatically split into orders by the delivery date that was saved. The customer can save the delivery date during the checkout process. The stock units' delivery date can also be saved or changed in the order itself. You can also use a <strong>group function</strong> to assign a delivery date to the orders.</p></td>
