</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Change status</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the status that you would like to set with the event procedure.<br>
<strong>Ignore <a href="/en/order-processing/orders/managing-sales-orders#delivery-order">delivery orders</a>: If you use the </strong>Change status** procedure for an order that includes delivery orders, then the status of the delivery orders will also be changed by default. Place a check mark next to this option if you only want the status of the main order to be changed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Change flag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the flag that you would like to set with the event procedure.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Change dunning level</strong></p></td>
