<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Assign sales representative to order</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">This procedure saves a sales representative in an order. The sales representative is assigned based on the order recipient’s zip code. In order for a sales representative to be assigned, you have to save a range of zip codes in the sales representative’s customer data. The sales representative’s ID is saved, not the name.<br>
